{
  "stem": "16106.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was talking about [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when [NON-ENGLISH] was taken, his mother went absolutely mad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all the Vilna girls were sleeping in one bunch.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They just threw themselves over her so the, the Germans shouldn't hear her screams.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Tried to choke her or hid her head in the chest, and-- and then they somehow got her husband over.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember him come, this handsome young man, and his face was-- I, I don't know how to describe it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Is, is the horror in his face.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then the woman-- the lady broke lose-- loose.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she ran all over the camp yelling, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I see her running.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She had long legs and long hair and a kerchief which flew in the wind.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she was yelling, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then the Germans said, OK, we take you to your [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was the last we saw from-- of her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "One more memory from Kaiserwald which was outstanding, it was in the beginning when they still came over from-- on Sundays.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we had loudspeakers, and she used to pipe in music.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And since it was Germany, we got the best.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was Wagner and Beethoven and you name it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And here we are standing on, in Kaiserwald, and it plays Ninth-- the Ninth Symphony by Beethoven over there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they're singing, [SINGING IN GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there was one German Jewish guy who was just standing there, like-- in transfixed, listening to the symphony.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And an SS man walked by, and the guy didn't see him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the SS man gave him a kick because he didn't take his hat off or something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I, I watched that, and that's an-- one of those things that I remember.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
